            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "We have been associated with Greenfield Chennai international School for the last 8 years. My child started her schooling from Pre.K.G. It has been a rewarding and enriching experience for us. The academic as well as overall development in children are evident and consistent. Overall it has been a good decision 👍",
          "publisher": {
